rComments: Wonderful professor and very knowledgeable and amiable.

Took this class as an elective but really learned a lot. Professor Gough cares about his students, and is really clear at explaining things in lecture AND at giving very hints on what the exams are like. Keep up with the assignments, they're designed to help you and the exams use very similar questions. Get help if you need it. Didn't use textbook.
Amazing professor....took all his classes cause he was so interesting and organized...best prof I've had in my three years of University.

Amazing guy.  Very quiet but takes an interest in each student!  You are not a # in his class.  Made us write HTML in his class 10 years ago, got me into tech!  Very fair.  What a great prof and a great guy!
